<p>Whatever you choose to do, communicate your remote-pay philosophy sooner rather than later to employees. The decision to pay based on location (or not) affects team membersâ€™ livelihoods. Be transparent about your plans so they can prepare for the future alongside your company.</p></div>";s:10:"post_title";s:58:"3 questions to ask before adopting location-based salaries";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:168:"To successfully execute location-based salaries, you have to weigh a number of variables. Answer these questions to determine whether this makes sense for your company.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:81:"httpswww-charthop-comblogbest-practicesquestions-adopting-location-based-salaries";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2022-05-02 10:45:56";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2022-05-02 10:45:56";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:138:"https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/%content_type%/%resource_category%/3-questions-to-ask-before-adopting-location-based-salaries/";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:9:"resources";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}